body:
Morning/Evening everyone!

I have come up with an idea to connect players and staff more, with this fun game.
So, the objective is for all users (Regular, donators and even retired), to post number by number, no more than one number per post, to reach the target before a Mod says "a quote from iMercury's topic" and then you start over.
All staff are allowed, but don't camp and post every time you see someone new post, it has to be fun for all of us!
Once someone reaches the goal, they add 10 to the original target.
The first target it 10, if you reach this without staff managing to post anything it would then advance to 20. 
If a staff member posts, then you start over to the last target.
As you only say a number also say a little message or something, if you want.

Enjoy! ;)

RIP
